claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A three-column table listing influenza vaccine types (Egg-based IIV4s, ccIIV4, RIV4, LAIV4) alongside their respective contraindications and precautions. The table presents contraindications and precautions for different influenza vaccine types and contains no information on antigenic match or strain selection procedures, and thus does not support the claim. Note: Image is clear but contains only safety guidance, not data on antigenic matching or WHO/FDA strain selection.
